    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "yeah i get the \"what you can't see\" part. but are there specific types of flaws or weird little issues that happen inside the mix itself? like, are there things that can get \"trapped\" or mess things up from the inside even if the rebar is okay?",
      "source": "evaluator"
